Class GenericEvent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GenericEvent>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BreakEvent, Event

    @Entity(name="GENERIC_EVENT")
public abstract class GenericEvent
extends EntityWithLongKey
implements java.lang.Comparable<GenericEvent>
    This JPA class represent a generic event structure, it is to be implemented by both event and break event classes
